_data.title: Forest
_data.body:
This is a forest, with trees in all directions around you.

You hear the chirping of a song bird in the distance.

[[East|Lost]]
[[West|Lost]]

_data.title: West of House
_data.body:
This is an open field west of a white house, with a boarded front door. 

There is a small mailbox here.

A rubber mat saying 'Welcome to Zork!' lies by the door.

[[West|Forest]]
[[Look at door.|The Door]]
[[Look at mat.|The Mat]]

_data.title: The Door
_data.body:
I see nothing special about the door.

[[back|West of House]]

_data.title: Lost
_data.body:
This is a forest, with trees in all directions around you.

You hear, you guessed it.  More birds...

Face it, you're lost.  Better start over.

[[Start Over|West of House]]
